title: Unique Apartment at The Summit View Apartments
posting_body: ['Property Address', '1329 Grand Ave - C | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available: 09/02/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Unique Apartment at The Summit View Apartments', 'This apartment is a unique garden-level apartment.', 'It provides a cool place to escape the sun in the summer and stays cozy & warm in the winter.', 'This particular apartment is very open and features a claw foot bathtub, exposed partial brick wall in the living room, exposed pipes, tiled and carpeted floor, and the bedroom has spacious.', 'walk-in closet.', 'The kitchen has been updated with newer cabinets, a breakfast bar, and updated lighting.', 'Sitting atop a ridge between the historic Summit and Grand Avenues at Hamline, this quaint pair of buildings has everything you are looking for.', 'Convenient to many local shops and restaurants, this location is also within easy reach of major highways and public transportation.', '1329 Grand Ave offers a renovated laundry room and bike storage.', 'Ask about our off-street parking availability.', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', ' Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Heat Paid', 'Water Paid', 'Trash Paid', 'Recycling Paid', 'Clubhouse and Fitness Center within Walking Distance', 'Controlled Entry', 'On-site Laundry', 'On Busline', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 650', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $920.00', 'Available: 09/02/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
